# Financial Risk Capital Adequacy Policy Liability Reinsurance Aggregate Amount

## identifier
de4919

## type
float

## definition
Report the aggregated value of the Policy Liability for all related product groups, as calculated by the capital adequacy standard, ceded under reinsurance. These are the guaranteed liabilities under life insurance policies on the basis of assumptions which are more conservative (anticipate a more adverse experience) than best estimate and solvency assumptions.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.CapitalAdequacy.PolicyLiabilityReinsuranceAggregate.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
